well, one job is already marked as failure
so I think this will be rejected by bors. but we'll see...

simulacrum said:

I don't see any evidence of bors going wrong, but CI certainly isn't behaving right

sorry, that's what I meant -- not bors specifically, but the entire interacting system of bors and CI and whatever :D
I think the two failure messages are for https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/pull/85557#issuecomment-846391746 and https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/pull/85557#issuecomment-846396873, respectively.
okay looks like it was just me (and the logbot) being confused :)
